Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.59,0:00:08.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這種躁動不安的感覺到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:11.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼要來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:14.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和關原有著同樣的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.09,0:00:16.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人反胃的戰爭的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.08,0:00:27.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找 把他們找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 吉爾德萊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.91,0:00:33.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這臭味 是漂流者的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:38.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,殺掉 把漂流者都殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.28,0:00:41.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要在無花果結果之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓它枯萎殆盡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:51.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被我找到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被我找到了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:12.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,散發著臭味的漂流物們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.41,0:01:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 出來吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:22.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我會漂亮地把你們燒得手舞足蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.64,0:01:27.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你用的這奇怪的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:30.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是妖術之類的東西麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:38.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:50.20,difters-op,,0,0,0,,發動引擎 給我動力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:54.67,difters-op,,0,0,0,,踩下油門 奏響福音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:55.38,difters-op,,0,0,0,,歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:55.38,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}sing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.12,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾馳 在這蜿蜒曲折中突進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:12.06,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.18,0:02:15.56,difters-op,,0,0,0,,這是颶風般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.73,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.11,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:23.57,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:29.41,difters-op,,0,0,0,,即使已超速 也無法捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:34.17,difters-op,,0,0,0,,引擎全開 全身繃緊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:34.92,difters-op,,0,0,0,,和我一同
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:34.92,difters-op,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,72.6)\fs43.5}everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.93,0:02:48.43,difters-op,,0,0,0,,疾馳 在這蜿蜒曲折中突進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.85,difters-op,,0,0,0,,已欲罷不能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:55.27,difters-op,,0,0,0,,這是颶風般的快感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.15,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.69,difters-op,,0,0,0,,感受到了這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:03.07,difters-op,,0,0,0,,正是狂奔的颶風
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(199.2,111.9)\fad(450,500)}第七幕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.18,0:03:13.81,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(357.6,249)\fad(450,500)}Chaos Diver
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:21.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 你們這些男人就集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可別把弓給落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:26.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,女人和小孩就逃往森林之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:26.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要去把騎兵給擊潰了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:31.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:34.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:36.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但我打敗騎兵隊的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在三千世界裡是無人能及的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:45.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的對手好像
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾德萊 把那個不男不女的傢伙給殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我來燒死這邊的漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 祝你旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然能把牆壁給砍破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.25,0:04:23.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼怪力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是武藏坊一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.80,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}\N註：武藏坊弁慶，源義經的家臣。他的經歷經常被當\N做小說的素材，為武士道精神的傳統代表人物之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.72,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(957.6,941.4)}Drifters
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:33.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王大人廢滅世界的障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流物就由我們來全部燒燬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.22,0:04:42.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就是那個眼鏡娘所說的廢棄物麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:45.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是群無法正常交流的瘋子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你到底是男還是女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:06.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,靈活的黃猴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你已無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你要怎麼做啊 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.34,0:05:15.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:18.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看我把你們燒成真正的廢棄物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,魔導結社 十月機關
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,保護漂流者乃我們的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:52.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 你也會使用妖術麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.67,0:05:55.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那個 我只能放出石壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:58.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 只剩兩張而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是大師傅大人的話就可以做出各種各樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我修行未夠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:08.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.57,0:06:13.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼啊 被救一命的人可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:15.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,別 別這樣啦 快把頭抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:21.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看 火還燒得正旺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人也還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可不是做那種事情的場合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.75,0:06:27.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是如果不先行此禮的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到時就無法這麼乾脆了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:36.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那個傢伙會用可怕的法術
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.05,0:06:39.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但他的戰鬥經驗應該很淺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:41.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是個新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:45.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼 為什麼你會得出這般結論
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是只是直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:56.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那傢伙是在炫耀自己獲得的這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:00.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在讓居於某處的某人見識一下這股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:04.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我獲得了這樣的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:05.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,關注我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:07.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:09.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是新兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,初次上陣突入敵陣戰鬥的人頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.88,0:07:15.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,取之 容易至極
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這點很可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:23.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他這個時代的日本武士的笑容裡都是感謝與死亡共存
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:27.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你說還能再放出兩次那個牆壁對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:33.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就按照我說的放出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:37.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,放完之後 你就往森林逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.68,0:08:01.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪…怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:05.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然那個巨大的騎士是個怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那個與一的人也不相上下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那個人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對 那樣就沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:26.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥很愉悅吧 與一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:31.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,人是為了發揮自己的才能才生於此世的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的才能不就是賜死的才能麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,可沒有閒暇給你射扇子了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.63,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}\N註：那須與一在屋島上的一箭射中了船上\N少女的扇子，而這一箭留下了千古佳話。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.60,0:08:54.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是吉爾德萊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,笑容也消失了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:08:59.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經射中他好幾箭了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:01.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,應該也有幾箭打中他要害了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:09.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的旅途現在還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我現在還不能倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:15.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 就如同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈哈 就像是弁慶一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是令人超懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.89,0:09:32.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,注意 大家聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,第六天魔王大人主講的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:38.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,連猴子都能做到的屠殺騎兵講座 開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好地聽的話 會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然騎兵是非常可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:46.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實一點都不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:49.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你們想說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.04,0:09:53.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,突襲 利用機動力迂迴作戰什麼的 可是超級可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.17,0:09:57.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他們這樣上了頭地在森林裡面追擊我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:01.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,連步兵都沒有 這樣就超不可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:03.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沖得這麼猛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:07.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,樹木還會限制他們的路線
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:12.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 設置一點障礙就可以讓他們停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:16.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,零散幾個騎兵跑進森林裡面可是等於自殺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.81,0:10:19.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我在伊勢的時候也被這招給害慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.69,0:10:20.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,行了 放箭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,佔據高地的話就已經等同於勝利了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,課程結束
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:33.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一…一轉眼就
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我回憶起長篠的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,強大的騎兵被拿火槍的雜兵打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕因為進化了的火槍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士和武士的時代會落下帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不管發生什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:55.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要在這裡製造大量的火槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:04.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是真正是怪物的那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:07.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,廢城正在燃燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:16.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,跑哪去了 到底跑哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:18.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底藏到那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:22.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快出來 快出來啊 漂流物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話 不然的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是森林還是城 一切的一切都要被我燃盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:33.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣的話我就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:39.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,無論再怎麼荒涼 那也是我的城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:45.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:48.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這下 已經無處可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:05.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 我是不會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真不懂吸取教訓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:26.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己的退路…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎 瘋了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:33.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 薩摩藩裡沒有一個士兵是理智的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:43.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人頭我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:46.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自己斷絕了自己的退路
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:48.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙到底怎麼了 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.05,0:12:50.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼 怎麼 一心赴死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:53.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,動手 奧爾米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這真是 太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是 什麼 什麼 什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.86,0:13:09.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把本來用於防禦的石壁的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:12.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不是用作防禦而是進攻的發射台上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.65,0:13:13.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:18.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然大師傅也告訴過我武士都是些不可理喻的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.54,0:13:22.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是捨棄了自己的生命然後眼中只有別人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:28.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了功名  還有「砍下敵方首級」這一意識長出了四肢一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.34,0:13:32.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣不就像是…廢棄物一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:34.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在城裡是一定會有那個的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:37.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就站在裡面等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.64,0:13:39.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:47.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,水 是水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:56.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那麼的需要 那麼的希望 那麼的渴望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:02.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.12,0:14:06.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女 在火焰中淨化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 魔女正被火焰所吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:14.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,戰場上扮成男人 結果卻是個魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:15.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是滑稽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:16.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,兩腿之間都被燒掉了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的你到底是男人還是女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.56,0:14:22.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧利安的魔女 讓我們看清楚點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡和人類是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:28.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是 魔女…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:32.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明為了人民 為了法國
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:36.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了神明而戰鬥過來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:14:59.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被人們所拋棄的你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼 你不是女人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:21.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一介女流為何要穿著鎧甲參加戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,女人的頭顱當不了功績
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 回去梳妝打扮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:33.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你 像你這種人懂什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,對於為了拯救法國的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為了基督 為了信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:43.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我們戰鬥至今的一切你怎麼可能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.65,0:15:54.73,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.23,0:15:58.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,法國這國家的名字我聽都沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:00.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 基督到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是費勁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:06.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,南蠻人總是不知道在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.00,0:16:08.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今只能快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:12.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個拿槍的武士的人頭砍下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:18.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不下人頭的話 就沒有臉面見江東父老了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼還不死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好 射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.53,0:17:27.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 不能讓與一死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.83,0:17:29.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快射 快射 快射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是不死之身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:37.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 這個世上沒有不死的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:43.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,萬物必有終焉 一定有辦法殺死他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:46.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快射 快射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:50.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的就像是弁慶一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:09.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:11.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:14.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如此憎恨這個世界嗎 廢棄物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:30.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被世界所拋棄的 陰魂不散的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,這是最後的彈夾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:40.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個來完工吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.72,0:19:08.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8)}快 小心點 此地不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.50,0:19:39.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.57,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(775.2,934.2)}La Pucelle
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:05.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,「少女」她去不了天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:09.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因為被當做異端和魔女而處以火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.86,0:20:11.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只能墮入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:15.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也跟隨著進入地獄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:19.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讓我犯下更多能讓我墮入地獄的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.29,0:20:23.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在地獄裡等我吧 貞德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:28.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 「少女」她並沒有墮入地獄而是來了這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:36.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但早已不是「少女」的她 必定要墮入地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:40.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這次就讓我先走一步 在地獄裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.06,0:20:43.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德 祝你一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.32,0:20:58.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 果然是用相同質量的鹽…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.58,0:21:02.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.50,0:21:09.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:13.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米道術師 幹得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:15.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:20.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是誰 不 「你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.52,0:21:24.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是憎恨著廢棄物的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:30.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾米的師傅 魔導結社「十月」的首領
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:33.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,支持著你們漂流者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:35.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被授予了消滅那些不應該存在於這個世上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.78,0:21:40.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,稱作「廢棄物」的傢伙這一使命的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.33,0:21:44.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼你也是「漂流者」對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.25,0:21:47.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,名字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:52.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,安倍 晴明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:03.35,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your way 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.31,0:22:03.35,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}開拓你的道路 向著拂曉之空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.61,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodthirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:07.61,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:12.57,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滾る心に刃と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.77,0:22:12.57,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}灼熱翻騰的心中之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:19.70,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}無に成る大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.74,0:22:19.70,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高舉心無旁騖的大義之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:31.17,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}陽炎は揺れるシンフォニー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:31.17,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}熱浪就如晃蕩的交響樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:41.18,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声　響く三日月夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:41.18,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌聲 在新月之夜下蕩漾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:44.52,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}こんなにくべる炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:44.52,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
